"    Email",
"   </a>",
"  </div>",
" </div>",
" <div class=\"graphic\">",
"  <div class=\"figure\" style=\"width: 575px\">",
"   <div class=\"ttl\">",
"    CT images of biologic lung volume reduction",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"cntnt\" style=\"width: 555px; height: 629px; background-image: url(data:image/jpeg;base64,);\">",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    Coronal computer tomography images obtained in the supine position at full lung inflation showing treatment site at baseline (pretreatment) and 6 weeks after low-dose (patients 1-4) and high-dose (patients 5-8) biologic lung volume reduction therapy. Numbering on the scans corresponds to treated sites showing evidence of scarring reactions.",
"    <div class=\"footnotes\">",
"     BioLVR: biologic lung volume reduction; HD: high dose; LD: low dose.",
